node.text:
Those stars and stripes looked good on the @cincinnati_inc Chevy on Sunday!

After @kylelarsonracin's hard run @mispeedway, the No. 5 driver has now finished top-three in 10 of the last 14 races this year. 🔥

node.text:
4️⃣ 0️⃣ 0️⃣ miles of high-speed action are complete @mispeedway!

@williambyron crossed the line in second, followed by @kylelarsonracin in third, @chaseelliott9 in eighth and @alex_bowman in 16th.

His quick work marks stage win No. 17 for the organization so far this year.
